<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266190>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 6. Mniotype, Mniopamea, Polymixis ssp. adults. 1. M. ripa sp. n., male, holotype, China, W. Sichuan, Litang (PGM / HNHM); 2. M. ripa sp. n., female, paratype, China, W. Sichuan, Litang (PGM); 3. M. melanodonta, male, China, Shaanxi, Tsinling Mts (PGM); 4. M. gandhara, female, Pakistan, Karakoram, Naltar valley (PGM); 5. P. b e a t a, male, Tibet [China], S. W. Himalaya, Nyalam (PGM); 6. P. re m o t a, female, China, W. Sichuan, Daocheng (ASV)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/266190/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266191>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7 – 9. Mniotype ssp. male genitalia. 7. M. ripa sp. n., male, holotype, China, W. Sichuan, prep. PGY 4379 m (PGM / HNHM); 8. M. ripa sp. n., male, paratype, China, W. Sichuan, prep. PGY 4297 m (PGM); 11. M. melanodonta, male, China, Shaanxi, prep. PGY 4404 m (PGM)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/266191/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266193>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 15. Mniotype, Mniopamea ssp. female genitalia. 13. M. ripa sp. n., female, paratype, China, W. Sichuan, prep. PGY 4380 f (PGM); 14. M. melanodonta, female, China, Shaanxi, prep. PGY 4403 f (PGM); 15. M. gandhara, female, Pakistan, Karakoram, prep. PGY 4401 f (PGM); Figure 16. China, West Sichuan, near Litang, the type locality of M. ripa sp. n.: 4000 m, N 29 ° 49.136 ′, E 100 ° 20.576 ′." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/266193/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.266192>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10 – 12. Mniotype, Polymixis, Mniopamea ssp. male genitalia. 10. M. draudti, male, China, Sichuan, prep. PGY 4035 m (PGM); 11. P. beata, male, Tibet [China], S. W. Himalaya, prep. PGY 1895 m (PGM); 12. M. cashmirensis, male, Pakistan, Karakoram, prep. PGY 4397 m (PGM)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/266192/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

